Package com.cognifide.qa.bb.qualifier

  • Annotation Types Summary 
    Annotation Type Description
    Cached
    Annotation used in tandem with FindBy, FindyBys, FindAll for injecting List of PageObjects.
    CurrentFrame
    Use this annotation to have Bobcat inject a PageObject's field with the current frame.
    CurrentScope
    Use this annotation to have Bobcat inject your field with WebElement that represents current scope.
    FindPageObject
    This annotation allows to find page object if identifier was added in PageObject annotation on type
    Frame
    This annotation can be added to any page object class or any method in page object.
    Global
    Add this annotation to any field annotated with any of the Find annotations.
    PageObject
    PageObject is a central concept of Bobcat.
    Retry
    Add this annotation to any test method which you want to rerun after failure
